        "rich_text_hQwUGz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Diamonds don’t always have to be for grand occasions. Every woman deserves timeless jewelry that elevates her look, even on a routine day. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown DIamond Jewellery\">Lab Grown Diamond jewellery</a> lets you go bold without making a compromise. We curated a range of fine online diamond jewellery made out of gold and platinum under 25k so that your sparkle never fades! Here are some top must-haves that are versatile and timeless:</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9gHtBX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Round Diamond Pear-Shape Stud Earrings",
          "settings": {
