        },
        "image_with_text_yWxFFz": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Half_Diamond_Butterfly_Pendant.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Add this whimsical charm to your everyday look with this half diamond butterfly jewellery pendant. This minimal, dainty and feminine pendant looks gorgeous on holiday outfits, beach wear, and looks chic in your daily routine. It is subtle yet memorable, making it perfect for your signature wear. Next time, a person spots a butterfly, the thought of you will flutter through their mind. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
