            "text": "<p>There’s always one piece of jewelry in a woman’s collection that she reaches for to pair with every outfit. The Linear Spark Chain Bracelet is that trendy jewellery. It is lightweight, secure and looks dainty and sleek with every outfit.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
